---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---
<BaseLayout title="About | C-Mind">
  <section class="hero">
    <h1>About C-Mind</h1>
    <p class="muted" style="max-width: 720px;">
      C-Mind was created to address gaps in access, engagement, and continuity
      of mental health support by leveraging advances in artificial intelligence
      responsibly and ethically.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2>Our Approach</h2>
    <p style="max-width: 720px;">
      Our work is grounded in scientific evidence, implementation awareness,
      and real-world healthcare needs. We emphasize collaboration with clinicians,
      researchers, and care organizations to ensure appropriate deployment and impact.
    </p>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
